desc: QY9 TONIC Syrup is HIGHEST QUININE low sugar Tonic concentrate. Sweetened only with honey and Truvia (tm) sweetener. QY9 Tonic is therapeutic, with a host and known health benefits. Please read our blog posts at QY9Tonic.com for more information on the benefits of Quinine used in moderation.

layout.text: QY9 Tonic is a therapeutic style quinine tonic concentrate for use as an alcoholic mixer or as a daily non alcoholic immuno supporting tonic, sweetened only with honey and Truvia (tm) sweetener. Just add 1-3 oz to your favorite sparkling water to create the most delicious tonic around, without all the sugar! Brewed with a splash of red grapefruit, citrus extracts and spices, it's truly heaven in a glass!
